column3: Great calculator. I use it for physics problems and it readliy aids in the soving of these problems. I recomend this app. Thank you.
The scientific calculators i bought have certain functions.  This calculator had those and a few more. Came in handy when my solar power calculator wouldn't work when there was not enough light.
I use it for physics when I dont have a calculator. Love It!
For a free scientific calculator, it's legit.  Took a while to get 100% used to it, but I use it all the time now.
Everything you think you need in a basic scientific calculator.
Very  nice and having a lot of calculation options
